Major update version 6.0 New: Based on the SwiftUI architecture all source code has been rewritten to achieve the best performance on the iOS system. New: New interface design. Customisable user interface theme select background images text color and size etc. New: Automatic language detection. New: Quick search function Google or Baidu . New: Create multiple conversation topics in the conversation translation page. New: Ancient Chinese language Wen Yan Wen texts can be translated into many different languages. New: Backup or restore bookmarks using the latest iCloud technology. New: Import bookmarks from the old version. New: Full screen text function.
